{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"StorageManager","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage_API\">Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager\"><code>StorageManager</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>estimate()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/persist\"><code>persist()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/persisted\"><code>persisted()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Storage 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/storage\"><code>Navigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator/storage\"><code>WorkerNavigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>安全上下文:</strong> 此项功能仅在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">安全上下文</a>(HTTPS), 一些 <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">支持的浏览器</a>.</p></div><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage_API\">Storage API</a>的 <strong><code>StorageManager</code></strong> 接口提供了用于管理数据本地存储权限和估算可用存储空间的接口。您可以使用<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/storage\"><code>navigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>或<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator/storage\"><code>WorkerNavigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>对此接口进行引用。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"storagemanager.estimate\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>StorageManager.estimate()</code></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"此功能仅在安全上下文（HTTPS）中可用\">安全上下文</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>返回一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>StorageEstimate</code></a>对象，此对象包含为你的域名预留的存储空间总大小和你已经使用的存储空间大小。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"storagemanager.persist\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/persist\"><code>StorageManager.persist()</code></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"此功能仅在安全上下文（HTTPS）中可用\">安全上下文</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>如果您的 user agent 能够将你域名下的数据持久保存，那么将返回一个状态为 resolve 的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"storagemanager.persisted\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/persisted\"><code>StorageManager.persisted()</code></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"此功能仅在安全上下文（HTTPS）中可用\">安全上下文</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>如果您的站点已经被授予可使用数据本地存储的权限，则返回一个状态为 resolve 的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a></p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://storage.spec.whatwg.org/#storagemanager","title":"Storage Standard"}],"query":"api.StorageManager"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.StorageManager","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"Storage API的 StorageManager 接口提供了用于管理数据本地存储权限和估算可用存储空间的接口。您可以使用navigator.storage (en-US)或WorkerNavigator.storage (en-US)对此接口进行引用。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"StorageManager","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"StorageManager","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"StorageManager","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"StorageManager","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"StorageManager","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"StorageManager","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/storagemanager","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/storagemanager/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager","title":"StorageManager"}],"pageTitle":"StorageManager - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}